cs.NI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper is about energy-efficient resource management in wireless sensor networks, which falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The proposed clustering algorithm involves data processing and analysis, which can be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS). The algorithm also utilizes image processing techniques, which can be classified under computer vision (cs.CV). Finally, the aim of prolonging the lifetime of WSN involves control and optimization, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY).
